Package: fp-extra
Architecture: i386
Depends: fp-compiler (= #PACKAGEVERSION#), fp-rtl (= #PACKAGEVERSION#)
Description: Free Pascal Extra Packages
 Some different packages for the Free Pascal Compiler
 Bindings to libraries:
